title: Leo By Zenith E-Juice
description: The distinctive fruity flavors of Zenith E-Juice have been developed over years of testing, reimagining, and perfecting. Once again, the quality of premium ingredients was put to the test as only the freshest, most natural fruit flavors were carefully chosen to blend with the mild but balancing flavor of milk. The Leo e-juice flavor is a tribute to one of all-time favorite breakfast cereals and strikes the ideal harmony between sweetness, creaminess, and fond memories of childhood.
